Author: whooptidooo
Text: Saaame! I ate nothing but healthy proteiny shit yesterday and reached my BMR levels. And despite all the coffee guzzling I got really snAaAcky, ate a box of wafers I didn't even like and forced myself to sleep so I wouldn't go rummaging around for more.  I hate how it's easier when you're fasting/restricting completely and just surviving on negligible liquid cals.
